{"tid":1258342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"逾千市民遊行到19領事館　南非總領事稱將信件交總統","createTime":"2019-06-26T05:13:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T05:57:40.000Z","uid":48093,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"45a0c909f4a28a4a70294d1ba2755f2f5d8e1b2b","tid":1258342,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T05:13:54.000Z","msg":"超過一千名市民響應網上號召，以靜默遊行方式，前往19個駐港總領事館遞信請願，爭取國際關注香港情況。<br />\n<br />\n遊行人士自製多國語言的標語，又準備不同語言的請願信。不少領館人士都有派代表出席，其中南非駐港澳總領事表示，會將信交予總統，再作出回應。至於俄羅斯駐港總領事館則沒有代表接信，由商場職員代為接信。<br />\n<br />\n遊行隊伍分成3個小隊，分別前往位於中環、灣仔及銅鑼灣的領事館，預計下午4時前會完成行動。沿途有市民舉起大拇指支持，認為行政長官林鄭月娥令香港人團結，也有市民指罵遊行人士對香港沒有貢獻。有司機則認為遊行人士阻礙交通，不斷響號。"},{"pid":"7507d1861b796913536d177d1c5bbe74dc4f68a7","tid":1258342,"uid":29128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T05:14:38.000Z","msg":"！！！今晚 （626） 愛丁堡 8PM 不見不散 ！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1258230/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1258230/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"0d1555f8f9a77d28b6b8a66215a77a87e5196004","tid":1258342,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T05:15:28.000Z","msg":"南非<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80ec36f6c29952c2270b969f8952eafd114514ff","tid":1258342,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T05:26:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"441e0268ad4ad32056f9c906c9a828e141f1b31c","tid":1258342,"uid":31151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T05:29:25.000Z","msg":"話撚左揾俄佬晒鳩氣架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p